    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is, quite simply, the finest example of its kind currently on the market. Meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, the exterior boasts a mirror-like depth to the paint, free of even the smallest stone chips or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin retains its original showroom scent; the premium leather seats remain supple with no visible wear, and every electronic component functions with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, accompanied by a comprehensive folder of every service record since day one. From the pristine undercarriage to the untouched alloy wheels, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a piece of automotive perfection that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line.",
      "price": 48500.0,
